org.checkerframework.dataflow.cfg.node

Class SynchronizedNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.checkerframework.dataflow.cfg.node.Node
      • org.checkerframework.dataflow.cfg.node.SynchronizedNode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.plumelib.util.UniqueId

    public class SynchronizedNode
extends Node
    This represents the start and end of synchronized code block. If startOfBlock == true it is the node preceding a synchronized code block. Otherwise it is the node immediately after a synchronized code block.
